{"tid":749480,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"(紀念禮物)蒙太奇照片合併","createTime":"2018-07-20T05:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T21:39:19.000Z","uid":55340,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64720ac2e55a57b090c212565ab0e797c0bdd3cb","tid":749480,"uid":55340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"用多張相合成一張 可以印出黎<br />\n例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://host.easylife.tw/files/Mosamic_TheTrumanShow.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhost.easylife.tw%2Ffiles%2FMosamic_TheTrumanShow.jpg&h=31d2add3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/130633_6fdebedc37545b9fc11b77bc284c7d1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F130633_6fdebedc37545b9fc11b77bc284c7d1b.jpg&h=fa900cca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n適合情侶 家人 朋友送禮 整返張獨一無二屬於你地既回憶<br />\n建議圖片庫越多越好 整出黎個效果好<br />\n如果唔滿意可以用Photoshop再執色<br />\n我自己用Photocap 6.0<br />\n傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pkstep.com/archives/10640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pkstep.com%2Farchives%2F10640&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w09tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=62db7a8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pkstep.com/archives/10640</a><br />\n<br />\n希望有人會岩用<br />\n應該無人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57a7ccf036eb7f91fcff52c7199d847eabc77a75","tid":749480,"uid":23953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://effectphoto.blogspot.com/2015/09/create-mosaic-photo-collage-with-gimp.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feffectphoto.blogspot.com%2F2015%2F09%2Fcreate-mosaic-photo-collage-with-gimp.html%3Fm%3D1&d=ZswPy%2BAChJBw01jT6W8w09tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=bcf7303a\" target=\"_blank\">https://effectphoto.blogspot.com/2015/09/